<div class="app-container">

<div class="page-header">
    <h1>Application Received!</h1>
</div>

<div class="content-container">
<div class="content-primary">

<div class="app-section">
    <h2>Thank you!</h2>
    <p>Your hosting application for <strong>[% site_name | html %]</strong> (<code>[% domain_name | html %]</code>) has been received and is pending review by our team.</p>
    <p>A confirmation has been sent to <strong>[% email | html %]</strong>.</p>
</div>

<div class="app-section">
    <h3>What happens next?</h3>
    <ol>
        <li>Our admin team reviews your application (usually within 1 business day).</li>
        <li>We create your site and configure the DNS.</li>
        <li>You will receive an email when your site is live at <code>[% domain_name | html %]</code>.</li>
        <li>Log in with username <strong>[% username | html %]</strong> to manage your site.</li>
    </ol>
</div>

<div class="form-actions">
    <a href="[% c.uri_for('/') %]" class="btn btn-primary">Return to Home</a>
</div>

</div>
</div>

</div>
